comment:
Every time I see AH on court steps, after The Sun libel case, I always love the look on her sister, Whitneys, face, looking at the back of AH's head. There's no joy. No relief. Just Whitney, boring her eyes into the back of AH's head. Why is she looking like that? Because her sister made her lie on the stand. Commit perjury. Know that her sister forced her to do something illegal.
If there's a retrial here in the UK, and I desperately hope there is, all of these lies are gonna come back and kick Whitney in the head. And will she maintain her lies? Not a chance. Faced with prison time and a massive fine, Whitney's gonna drop her sister in it, all the way up to her neck. 
I love my sister, and would defend her to the enth degree. But if they said, "if you commit perjury, you're  going to be sharing a jail cell with a 400 pound gorilla called 'Bubba', who likes to wear lipstick", I'm going to sing like a bird, and gladly wave my sister off as she starts her 5 year sentence. She'll also be shi**ing herself cos of the Virginia trial, too.
That's if AH is not already in an Australian jail, having committed perjury for illegally taking her dogs there. The Australians are very hot on this, and knowingly lying to their government is an extremely bad idea.
One way or another, AH is going down, and she only has herself to blame. 😁👍🏻
